{
  "stem": "26609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He came back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the next morning, he had to come-- go back to work, to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Children were not allowed out of the camp, of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told he was a tall man, a big, tall man, with a big coat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was I think late autumn or early winter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took the child of five year, a little boy, under his coat, tied him around to his waist, covered him with his coat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how he marched up to them, up to there, to the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] where the camp was, both Nazi and Italians.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they hid there-- she didn't have to be-- there she could be hidden because he was-- they were afraid maybe some of Italians would give her out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they kept them in a house somewhere with the child and fed them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But a few months later, it is known that there was a rift between the Italians and Nazis, between Mussolini and Hitler.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know exactly the history, but it's known there was a rift between them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Italians-- the army had to go back to Italy, leave Germany-- actually, Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the German-- it was occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as they had to go back, my brother-in-law and my sister and my-- their child didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then the Germans took over and took him away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't need a Jew-- a translator.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had theirs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not [INAUDIBLE] didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't want a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he probably, because we never heard of him, killed him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my sister understood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It never came back that they killed him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She had no place where to go with the child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So she went out on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't think she was confused.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
